tool used to query DNS name servers
dig axfr {domain ex. bank.htb} @IP ex.10.10.11.79

ffuf : (fuzz faster u Fool) is a powerful tool used by penetester
	to discover hidden files and directory on web servers

Nmap: is a powerful network scanning tool

sudo nmap -sC -sV -vv -oA nmap/[file-name] [ip]

gobuster: a powerful directory listing tool
	-b 404,403 used to block all of 404 and 403 error codes


useful tool/website

https://gtfobins.github.io

cool command:
	ps -eaf --forest [to list all of the proccess in a forest view :)]
	ss -lnpt [to look at all open port :)]


Seclists Directory:
	/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content

